       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. PROJECT-SCHEDULER-LOADER.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01 FIRST-MINUTES PIC X(8).
       01 SECOND-MINUTES PIC X(8).
       01 THIRD-MINUTES PIC X(8).
       01 PHASE-LABEL PIC X(16).
       01 TOTAL-MINUTES PIC S9(5) COMP-5.
       LINKAGE SECTION.
       01 LNK-RESULT PIC S9(5) COMP-5.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION USING BY REFERENCE LNK-RESULT.
MAIN.
       MOVE "120" TO FIRST-MINUTES.
       MOVE "090" TO SECOND-MINUTES.
       MOVE "045" TO THIRD-MINUTES.
       MOVE "ASSEMBLY" TO PHASE-LABEL.
       COMPUTE TOTAL-MINUTES = FUNCTION NUMVAL(FIRST-MINUTES)
           + FUNCTION NUMVAL(SECOND-MINUTES)
           + FUNCTION NUMVAL(THIRD-MINUTES).
       IF PHASE-LABEL = "ASSEMBLY"
           ADD 15 TO TOTAL-MINUTES
       END-IF.
       MOVE TOTAL-MINUTES TO LNK-RESULT.
       GOBACK.
       END PROGRAM PROJECT-SCHEDULER-LOADER.
